served activity patterns.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Thies, Wibke", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kalko, Elisabeth K. V.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Schnitzler, Hans-Ulrich", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1483145f10c3b1671a2618e69a167385", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/d9c10546c5df4c74b90b16300569f5d1595915d5462fd4e7104789a1d7051c3a", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/VIE7ZEQ7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/VIE7ZEQ7", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/4a2ca47f6c19a0d3b66dd512480eb3b4!/b319291-321845", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "2", "pages": "331-338", "title": "Journal of Mammalogy", "volume": "87"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/1483145f10c3b1671a2618e69a167385"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:VIE7ZEQ7"}, {"identifier": "10.1644/05-MAMM-A-161R1.1"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_type": "recid", "pid_value": "14817629"}}]}}, "title": "INFLUENCE OF ENVIRONMENT AND RESOURCE AVAILABILITY ON ACTIVITY PATTERNS OF CAROLLIA CASTANEA (PHYLLOSTOMI